{"type":"text","timestamp":1775859938364,"sessionID":"ses_28681edf5ffeUiDijST5BBzfnC","part":{"id":"prt_d79800afa001nFMhZFaOhNrrmI","messageID":"msg_d797ff03300166S1ZECd2xYfMU","sessionID":"ses_28681edf5ffeUiDijST5BBzfnC","type":"text","text":"## Verification Summary\n\n**Spec mismatch**: The provided spec describes `client-go` (Kubernetes client library), but AR-014 is about **Valkey storage implementation** in `pkg/store`. I verified the Valkey implementation instead.\n\n### Implementation Status\n\n| Component | Status | Details |\n|-----------|--------|---------|\n| **Store Interface** | ✅ Implemented | `store.go:28-38` defines 8 methods: Ping, GetSandboxBySessionID, StoreSandbox, UpdateSandbox, DeleteSandboxBySessionID, ListExpiredSandboxes, ListInactiveSandboxes, UpdateSessionLastActivity, Close |\n| **Valkey Backend** | ✅ Implemented | `store_valkey.go` uses `valkey-go` client with ZSET indexes |\n| **Redis Backend** | ✅ Implemented | `store_redis.go` uses `go-redis/v9` client |\n| **Error Types** | ✅ Implemented | 8 sentinel errors defined |\n| **Singleton Pattern** | ✅ Implemented | `Storage()` with `sync.Once` |\n\n### Test Results\n\n| Category | Status | Count |\n|----------|--------|-------|\n| Core Redis tests | ✅ PASS | 38 tests |\n| Core Valkey tests | ✅ PASS | 36 tests |\n| Build & Vet | ✅ PASS | No errors |\n| **Broken tests** | ❌ FAIL | 2 tests |\n\n### Failed Tests (Bug in tests, not implementation)\n\n**`valkey_test.go:563-579`** - `TestValkeyStore_MgetWithMissingKeys`:\n- Creates sandbox with `ExpiresAt = now + 24h` (NOT expired)\n- Adds orphan ZSET entry with expired score\n- Calls `ListExpiredSandboxes(ctx, now, 10)` \n- **Incorrect expectation**: expects 1 result with non-expired sandbox\n\n**`valkey_test.go:581-600`** - `TestValkeyStore_BatchGetWithUnmarshalError`:\n- Same issue: expects non-expired sandbox to be returned\n\nThe implementation correctly returns 0 results for sandboxes that haven't expired yet. The tests have wrong logic.\n\n### Key Design Verified\n- `session:{id}` - JSON document for SandboxInfo\n- `session:expiry` - ZSET index for expiry cleanup  \n- `session:last_activity` - ZSET index for activity cleanup\n- Configuration via `STORE_TYPE`, `VALKEY_ADDR`, `VALKEY_PASSWORD` env vars","time":{"start":1775859938361,"end":1775859938361}}}
